titles.title: Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 5009.
Directing the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of the bill H.R. 5009.

action.text: Mr. Rogers (AL) asked unanimous consent to consider as introduced.

vote.text: On agreeing to the resolution Agreed to without objection.

action.text: Motion to reconsider laid on the table Agreed to without objection.

bill.summary: This concurrent resolution directs the Clerk of the House of Representatives to make a correction in the enrollment of H.R. 5009 (Servicemember Quality of Life Improvement and National Defense Authorization Act for Fiscal Year 2025) to amend the long title of the act.
